typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Every city needs trash cans. Currently, there are not enough of them, and because of this, citizens throw waste into nature or take it to their homes to dispose of it. We want a clean and tidy city, don't we? If you agree, vote."

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Light pollution is not a word you hear often, but it is a reality. Negative impact on flora and fauna, disruption of road users, energy inefficiency are just a few of the problems it brings. Smart lighting solves the problem! And for that... vote."
